{"tid":767954,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"煙鏟無煙係手.真係慘過肚痛無廁所","createTime":"2018-08-05T03:59:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-05T10:45:45.000Z","uid":119688,"like":37,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e6ff05ae067a5dbefbf7f5435302a6e9a9bd685a","tid":767954,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T03:59:00.000Z","msg":"身邊80%既人都食<br />\n一無煙果班煙鏟<br />\n屌你坐立不安 精神恍忽<br />\n叫佢好似無反應 唔識佢以為柏金遜<br />\n<br />\n心諗如果呢個世界無哂煙,真係暴動世界大戰<br />\n<br />\n剩係我屋企個垃圾廢老 24小時不離手 只有訓著左先會停<br />\n出門口得一個理由就係買煙  一世人就係比煙呢種垃圾物質困哂身<br />\n真係值得咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">煙鏟肺癌仆街死啦 屌你地老母啊而家</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"4ee2b42aaee734969671bcd82cee5430db3e6cc8","tid":767954,"uid":119688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T04:00:37.000Z","msg":"有個問題亦一直想知<br />\n煙鏟坐長途機點樣過呢<br />\n隨時發老脾迫降落喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60788519a13047dac052150e95264e0db0f4b199","tid":767954,"uid":68,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4ee2b42aaee734969671bcd82cee5430db3e6cc8","tid":767954,"uid":119688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T04:00:37.000Z","msg":"有個問題亦一直想知<br />\n煙鏟坐長途機點樣過呢<br />\n隨時發老脾迫降落喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T04:07:12.000Z","msg":"上機前食幾枝囉<br />\n<br />\n利申已戒"},{"pid":"ef4d77d050f364335efd38fc8799d9e2d685c38f","tid":767954,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60788519a13047dac052150e95264e0db0f4b199","tid":767954,"uid":68,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4ee2b42aaee734969671bcd82cee5430db3e6cc8","tid":767954,"uid":119688,"like":1,"dislike":0,